</FOOTNAME>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
H-point means hinge point: hip hinge point on an anthropomorphic manikin, measured with the seat in the rearmost position.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

